WEBVTT

00:09.543 --> 00:13.981
Soñar el sueño impossible.

00:14.014 --> 00:16.650
"The impossible dream."

00:16.684 --> 00:18.552
We did it, man.
Yeah.

00:18.586 --> 00:20.054
[Alarm beeping]
Gentlemen,
the dream is over.

00:20.088 --> 00:22.623
Uh, I pushed something and
sort of set the engine on fire,

00:22.656 --> 00:24.725
so we need to jump.
You said
you can fly a plane.

00:24.758 --> 00:27.628
In my heart, I thought I could,
but don't worry.

00:27.661 --> 00:28.996
There's
three parachutes.

00:29.029 --> 00:32.966
[Woman screaming]

00:35.936 --> 00:38.038
Okay, there's two parachutes
and obviously,

00:38.072 --> 00:39.740
I should take one,
because I'm more important!

00:39.773 --> 00:41.175
[Explosion]
Whoa!

00:41.209 --> 00:42.910
Lamar!
What the hell, man?!

00:42.943 --> 00:46.447
I'm sorry, but you know
it's true! Society needs me!

00:46.480 --> 00:49.917
I'm a genius! I create
timeless works of literature!

00:49.950 --> 00:52.186
Okay, I'll see you
around the Lodge, boys!

00:52.220 --> 00:55.389
Wait!
And don't forget
the scrolls!

00:55.423 --> 00:57.425
Lamar!
Geronimo!

00:57.458 --> 00:59.760
Wait! Wait!
Hold on!

00:59.793 --> 01:01.329
The scrolls!

01:04.165 --> 01:05.099
Hurry!

01:05.133 --> 01:06.567
But how are we
gonna do this?!

01:06.600 --> 01:07.901
We're gonna do it
together!

01:07.935 --> 01:09.837
Okay. Okay.
I won't let go!

01:09.870 --> 01:11.772
All right.
Go!

01:11.805 --> 01:15.176
**

